.TH TGLFS 1 "March 2026" "tglfs 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
tglfs \- authenticate with Telegram, search file cards, and download TGLFS files by UFID
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B tglfs
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] [\fICOMMAND\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B tglfs
is a global command-line client for authenticating with Telegram, searching TGLFS file cards in Saved Messages, and downloading current-format TGLFS files by UFID.
.PP
Run
.B tglfs help <command>
for subcommand-specific help.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B login
Authenticate with Telegram and persist the resulting session.
.TP
.B status
Show current config and Telegram authorization state.
.TP
.B logout
Remove the saved Telegram session.
.TP
.B search [query]
Search TGLFS file cards in Saved Messages.
.TP
.B download <ufid>
Download a current-format TGLFS file by UFID.
.TP
.B help [command]
Display help for a command.
.SH FILES
The CLI stores config and session files in OS-standard per-user app directories.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR tglfs-login (1),
.BR tglfs-status (1),
.BR tglfs-logout (1),
.BR tglfs-search (1),
.BR tglfs-download (1)
